{"id":"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator","title":"CheckboxRequiredValidator","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator\", \"name\": \"CheckboxRequiredValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L383-L415\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"checkboxrequiredvalidator\">CheckboxRequiredValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#checkboxrequiredvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7x5tn5x6ovr8p97q43fafwgc1\">該指令會藉助 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> 繫結把 <code>required</code> 驗證器新增到任何帶有 <code>required</code> 屬性的檢查框控制元件上。</p>\n\n  </section>\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9kcmpkcn1zt46hrz7stqgq0xa\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">表單驗證</a></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code>FormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code>ReactiveFormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"inherited-members-list\">\n  <h3 id=\"繼承自-requiredvalidator\">繼承自 <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator\">RequiredValidator</a></code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#繼承自-requiredvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#required\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@Input()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">required</span>: boolean | string</a></code>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"17wyquqz4x160dqtizixcj6wq\">使用範本驅動表單為複選框新增必填項驗證器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2g18prdhs0mfkjuhncjjhehf1\">以下範例顯示如何向附加到ngModel繫結的輸入新增複選框必填驗證器。</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"active\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> required&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n\n\n\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#checkboxrequiredvalidator\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#description\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#selectors\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#匯出自\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#繼承自-requiredvalidator\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#required\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L383-L415